---

<html>
	<Layout title="Charlie & Astro">
		<main>
			<h1>El diario de <span class="text-gradient">Blanca</span></h1>
			<p class="instructions">
				Para empezar entra aqu√≠ <code>Astro/src/pages</code> en tu proyecto.
				<strong>Code Challenge:</strong> Tweak the "Blanca Monokai"
			</p>
		</main>
		<br />
	</Layout>
	<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
		<Card
			href="https://docs.astro.build/"
			title="Documentaci√≥n üöÄ"
			body="Aprende como que ????"
		/>
		<Card
			href="https://astro.build/integrations/"
			title="Integraciones üåº"
			body="Supercharge your project with new frameworks and libraries."
		/>
		<Card
			href="https://astro.build/themes/"
			title="Themes üîâ"
			body="Explore a galaxy of community-built starter themes. "
		/>
